rComments: This was Prof. Dielh's first time lecturing at UofT. She isn't a bad professor, however, he accent makes her hard to understand some times; 15% midterm, 35% essay, and 50% exam. Lecture heavy and lots of readings by the 2nd week (60 pages per week). Overall, not a bad course but it is content heavy. The exam and midterm were straightforward.
